original_title: Monster High: Clawesome Double Feature - Escape From Skull Shores / Fright On
overview: It's time to "fang out" with your favorite ghoulfriends in this frightfully fabulous double feature straight from the latest scare-mester at Monster High(TM)! Everyone's ready for some monstrous fun in the sun during spring break in "Escape from Skull Shores". But when they find themselves shipwrecked on a totally strange island, Frankie Stein(TM) is taken by a mysterious Beast... who may just need a little rescuing of his own! Then it's time to pull together all the student bodies when a meddling normie tries to drive a stake into the imperfectly perfect harmony of Monster High(TM) in "Fright On!" It's up to Frankie Stein(TM), Clawdeen Wolf(TM), Draculaura(TM)and their fangtastic friends to prove that the culture clash of Fur and Fang is no longer an issue for this scary-cool student body.
title: Monster High: Clawesome Double Feature - Escape From Skull Shores / Fright On
